org.netbeans.api.editor.caret

Class CaretInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.api.editor.caret.CaretInfo

  • public final class CaretInfo
extends Object
    Immutable info about a single caret used in caret API - see EditorCaret.
    There is one-to-one reference between immutable caret info and mutable CaretItem. CaretItem is not accessible through the caret API and it's managed privately by EditorCaret. Once the caret item gets mutated its corresponding caret info becomes obsolete and new caret info instance gets created lazily.
    Since:
    2.6
    See Also:
    EditorCaret

        @NonNull
public Position.Bias getDotBias()
        Get a bias of the dot position which is either Position.Bias.Forward or Position.Bias.Backward depending on whether the caret biases towards the next character or previous one. The bias is always forward for non bidirectional text.
